name: Nearby
body:
### Introduction
This is a simple example for use [Nearby Messages API](https://developers.google.com/nearby/messages/overview).

Is a simple Android App with EditText, Button and Toast making in Android Studio.

### Official documentation
See official documentation in [Google Developers Page](https://developers.google.com/nearby/)
